creator: Special Matrimony
descriptionHtml:
Special Matrimony is a matchmaking app that is tailored towards individuals that are deaf, hard of hearing, autistic, visually impaired and those who may have additional support needs (Cerebral palsy, Spinal Injury, Amputee, Asperger’s syndrome, Tourette syndrome, etc).

Simple, easy and modern user-interface.

• Register for free
• View profiles near you
• Interact with users via Video call and Instant messaging!
• Send and receive virtual gifts.
• Enable and disable video call/chat features.
• Receive message notifications on the go.
• Filter through the Advanced search field
• Report, Block users & much more...

We aim to provide a safe and secure platform where individuals can connect and find potential matches. We take immense care of your beliefs, values and needs whilst arranging matchmaking.

Special Matrimony is an exclusive app for singles. Here you will find your perfect partner, matching your search preferences. When we start a relationship, honesty, loyalty, and mutual understanding between two individuals are required to coordinate.

We will be here to support you with your search and to ensure you have a pleasant experience using our platform. We feel proud to be a medium to bring love and happiness into your life.

Install the Special-Matrimony app today to find your special someone!
